{"tid":397475,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"（飲評人請進）覺唔覺飲品雪櫃向來都係一場廝殺？","createTime":"2017-09-12T13:33:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-12T15:03:13.000Z","uid":82558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ae835865cb3ea218fca335e66305ec48acf61f08","tid":397475,"uid":82558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T13:33:22.000Z","msg":"小弟習慣一興起就會去七仔買嘢飲，次次去都發覺飲品雪櫃裏面又有一番新景象，汰弱留強。咁小弟都會膽粗粗試吓新嘢嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，同埋有時新產品做推廣價，幾吸引<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，不過真心發覺新推出嘅飲品中伏率高達九成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，直頭係當顧客試毒咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （留番係雪櫃入面超過一年嘅飲品都係社會良心）。<br />\n<br />\n為免有人重蹈覆轍，所以小弟決定拋磚引玉。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/12/212942_3acb5672ba3d4e0a866e7a5eb987eecf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F12%2F212942_3acb5672ba3d4e0a866e7a5eb987eecf.jpg&h=c95e5ebc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\ncarbonated嘅乳酸飲品本身都係伏伏地（顏色又好似番梘水），但諗住新奇士應唔會太差（橙汁一向OK），結果真係唔掂，加菠蘿味真係好怪，chemical感好重，同櫃仲有隻白桃味（粉色），但應該都差別唔大。<br />\n樓下七仔賣緊10蚊，但應該唔會再試（除非流浪沙漠冇水飲）<br />\n新奇士都係專注做柑橘類生果喇，同埋乳酸同碳酸好似港女同毒男咁，真係冇咩事就唔好溝埋一齊，會直接bad end。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家分享一下，功德無量。"},{"pid":"0bcf4172e0c6199a8be8c5d5bd6e6836ecad78fc","tid":397475,"uid":9436,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T13:37:01.000Z","msg":"講咁多 明眼人一睇就知係伏啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d27126390c0623420e6eb55c670e701dd7e9ca4","tid":397475,"uid":33883,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T13:49:02.000Z","msg":"見到呢D明顯係整色整水既化學飲品, 稍為有常識既都唔會掂啦, 飲你唔死算你好彩架喇! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25c8169524a2601e2cf28ff2a6619b22ba58005c","tid":397475,"uid":55851,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T13:50:14.000Z","msg":"好柒你篇文打得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f75b63efaafe37ad36f65a20781ffcfe0330a047","tid":397475,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T13:53:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好柒你篇文打得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66d1a4c3dd62ecb44a638c46ca4f40ced4c0d48b","tid":397475,"uid":75100,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T14:01:15.000Z","msg":"日本乳酸飲品好撚多伏架，仲衰過香港台灣既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真係飲益力多/ 內地優益c好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b621b9f0e65e7556e189fcf0b152b48dfffaa3b","tid":397475,"uid":5846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T14:45:08.000Z","msg":"除左維他奶同茶，其他甜野我基本唔會睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b591f4ff7d04b27887ca3b79486ec3d00425621","tid":397475,"uid":44814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T15:03:13.000Z","msg":"有唔少新野其實都ok <br />\n睇個combination就大約知伏味濃唔濃<br />\n例如之前道地芒果綠茶都還可以 芒果味假左啲但可以接受 10蚊一枝算係咁"}]}